      "writtenOn": "2021-01-13T19:49:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Without chunked transfer encoding you\u0027ll need Content-Length header. The only way to get it is to compress everything into a memory buffer before sending it to the network. This buffer is unnecessary when using chunked encoding.",
